  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of Pierre, a work-from-home employee for the mysterious ¾ Infinity Corp. Your job is to run and monitor a prototype A.I code-named “Laplace”. Follow the corporation's email instructions, and be sure to keep an eye out for any anomalies that may appear around your living quarters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f7205507aa1bf02a069c061845ef20a.poster.avif?t=1749892254\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f7205507aa1bf02a069c061845ef20a.webm?t=1749892254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f7205507aa1bf02a069c061845ef20a.mp4?t=1749892254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully functioning in-game computer, complete with an internet browser, minigames, and a file system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No blood or gore. The environments will serve to unnerve you rather than graphic content.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short but jam-packed experience intended to be finished in under 30 minutes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An included guide for those just wanting to experience the story.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f32e91aeb25a266bc7d52e9463b93d8.poster.avif?t=1749892254\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f32e91aeb25a266bc7d52e9463b93d8.webm?t=1749892254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f32e91aeb25a266bc7d52e9463b93d8.mp4?t=1749892254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bonus Content</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore brand new areas, browse the internet, and learn more about the secrets of this alternative reality in the Steam release! Now with double the content of the original release.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of Pierre, a work-from-home employee for the mysterious ¾ Infinity Corp. Your job is to run and monitor a prototype A.I code-named “Laplace”. Follow the corporation's email instructions, and be sure to keep an eye out for any anomalies that may appear around your living quarters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f7205507aa1bf02a069c061845ef20a.poster.avif?t=1749892254\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f7205507aa1bf02a069c061845ef20a.webm?t=1749892254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f7205507aa1bf02a069c061845ef20a.mp4?t=1749892254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully functioning in-game computer, complete with an internet browser, minigames, and a file system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No blood or gore. The environments will serve to unnerve you rather than graphic content.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short but jam-packed experience intended to be finished in under 30 minutes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An included guide for those just wanting to experience the story.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f32e91aeb25a266bc7d52e9463b93d8.poster.avif?t=1749892254\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841470/extras/0f32e91